comment.author: 13935339@N05
comment._content: P-47D serial 42-22533 (coded QI-V underscored) of the 361st Fighter Squadron, 356th FG is damaged in a taxi accident at Martlesham Heath on 15 April 1944; pilot Frank A. Policelli apparently wasn't paying attention and ran the tail of his 'Jug' into a neighboring P-47.
